<view class="page-wrap">

  <view class="card">
    <view class="card-h">
      <text class="card-tag">NPV</text>
      <text class="card-title">现金流净现值 · 周期版</text>
    </view>
    <view class="card-body">
      公式: <text class="accent">NPV = Σ CF_t / (1+r)^t</text> · 但折现率 r 不是常数,
      它跟随你处在周期的哪个阶段而变。同一项目,绝望期更贵、乐观期更便宜 —
      这是本书第三章的核心洞察。
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="card-title" style="font-size:28rpx;">情景模板</view>
    <view style="margin-top:12rpx;">
      <view wx:for="{{scenarios}}" wx:key="name"
            class="phase-pill {{currentScenario===item.name?'active':''}}"
            bindtap="useScenario" data-name="{{item.name}}">{{item.name}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="muted" style="margin-top:16rpx;font-size:22rpx;">{{scenarioDesc}}</view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="card-title" style="font-size:28rpx;">现金流 (年 0 = 初始投资)</view>
    <view style="margin-top:16rpx;display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <view wx:for="{{cashflows}}" wx:key="*this" wx:for-index="i" class="cf-pill">
        <text class="muted">Y{{i}}</text>
        <input class="input-field" type="digit" value="{{item}}"
               data-idx="{{i}}" bindinput="onCfChange" />
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="card-title" style="font-size:28rpx;">基础折现率 (周期中性)</view>
    <view class="row" style="margin-top:16rpx;">
      <text class="result-value" style="font-size:40rpx;">{{baseRatePct}}%</text>
      <view class="btn btn-ghost" style="padding:12rpx 20rpx;font-size:22rpx;flex:0 0 auto;"
            bindtap="syncFromFred">
        {{fredSyncing?'同步中…':'📡 用实时 10Y'}}
      </view>
    </view>
    <slider min="1" max="20" step="0.5" value="{{baseRate100}}"
            activeColor="#f0b429" backgroundColor="#1f3a5f"
            block-color="#f0b429" block-size="20"
            bindchange="onRateChange" />
    <view class="muted" style="font-size:22rpx;">
      建议:衰退/绝望期 12–18%,正常周期 8–10%,乐观期市场只愿意接受 6–8%。
    </view>
    <view wx:if="{{fredSyncMsg}}" class="muted" style="font-size:22rpx;margin-top:8rpx;color:#22c55e;">
      {{fredSyncMsg}}
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="card-title" style="font-size:28rpx;">同一项目 · 4 个周期阶段下的 NPV</view>
    <view class="table">
      <view class="tr th">
        <text class="td">阶段</text>
        <text class="td">折现率</text>
        <text class="td">NPV</text>
      </view>
      <view wx:for="{{phaseRows}}" wx:key="key" class="tr">
        <text class="td"><text class="phase-pill {{item.key===bestPhase?'active':''}}">{{item.label}}</text></text>
        <text class="td muted">{{item.ratePct}}%</text>
        <text class="td {{item.npv>=0?'success':'danger'}}">{{item.npvFmt}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="card-title" style="font-size:28rpx;">关键观察</view>
    <view class="card-body">{{insight}}</view>
  </view>

</view>
